hopobject.body: Could you tell me my balance, please? medscape.com ceu Didn't she learn anything from Eva Longoria? Rosario Dawson became just the latest starlet to have a fashion faux pas while walking the famous red carpet stairs at the Cannes Film Festival on May 20, 2013. Donning a white Elie Saab gown with a thigh-high slit, the actress accidentally flashed her flesh-toned underwear to the crowd at the "As I Lay Dying" premiere. Realizing what happened, Dawson quickly tried to cover up. Lucky for the actress, she exposed a little less than Longoria ...
